The paper deals with computer vision tasks such as object detection and segmentation, which are typically covered under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of machine learning techniques to predict histograms of object sizes also suggests that the paper could be relevant to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper also mentions applications in biology and medicine, which could make it relevant to the computational biology (cs.CL) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories.
